  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_002",
    "speaker": "char_li_wen_xiu",
    "listener": "char_wa_er_la_qi",
    "text": "师父，你得不到心爱的人，就将她杀死。我得不到心爱的人，却不忍心让他给人杀了。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 1176,
    "line_end": 1176,
    "source_refs": [
      {
        "chapter": 1,
        "anchor": "李文秀对瓦耳拉齐说的话",
        "event_type": "resolution"
      }
    ],
    "rag_refs": [1]
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_003",
    "speaker": "char_ma_jia_jun",
    "listener": "char_li_wen_xiu",
    "text": "江南的杨柳，已抽出嫩芽了，阿秀，你独自回去吧，以后⋯⋯以后可得小心，计爷爷，计爷爷不能再照顾你了⋯⋯",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 1138,
    "line_end": 1138,
    "source_refs": [
      {
        "chapter": 1,
        "anchor": "马家骏临死前对李文秀说的话",
        "event_type": "resolution"
      }
    ],
    "rag_refs": [1]
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_004",
    "speaker": "char_ma_jia_jun",
    "listener": "char_li_wen_xiu",
    "text": "我⋯⋯我不是你计爷爷，我⋯⋯我⋯⋯",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 1116,
    "line_end": 1116,
    "source_refs": [
      {
        "chapter": 1,
        "anchor": "马家骏揭示真实身份",
        "event_type": "climax"
      }
