  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_007",
    "speaker": "char_su_pu",
    "listener": "char_li_wen_xiu",
    "text": "李英雄，李英雄，快出来。",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 1158,
    "line_end": 1158,
    "source_refs": [
      {
        "chapter": 1,
        "anchor": "苏普呼唤李文秀",
        "event_type": "resolution"
      }
    ],
    "rag_refs": [1]
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_008",
    "speaker": "char_a_man",
    "listener": "char_su_pu",
    "text": "你怎么老是叫她李英雄，不叫李姑娘？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 1164,
    "line_end": 1164,
    "source_refs": [
      {
        "chapter": 1,
        "anchor": "阿曼调侃苏普",
        "event_type": "resolution"
      }
    ],
    "rag_refs": [1]
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_009",
    "speaker": "char_su_pu",
    "listener": "char_a_man",
    "text": "李姑娘，她是女子吗？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 1164,
    "line_end": 1164,
    "source_refs": [
      {
        "chapter": 1,
        "anchor": "苏普不知道李文秀是女子",
        "event_type": "resolution"
      }
    ],
    "rag_refs": [1]
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_010",
    "speaker": "char_a_man",
    "listener": "char_su_pu",
    "text": "那时候我见到了她瞧着你的眼色，就知道她是姑娘。天下那会有一个男子，用这样的眼光痴痴的瞧着你！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 1166,
    "line_end": 1166,
    "source_refs": [
      {
        "chapter": 1,
        "anchor": "阿曼揭示李文秀是女子",
        "event_type": "resolution"
      }
    ],
    "rag_refs": [1]
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_011",
    "speaker": "char_wa_er_la_qi",
    "listener": "char_li_wen_xiu",
    "text": "我要你永远在这里陪我，永远不离开我⋯⋯",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 1198,
    "line_end": 1198,
    "source_refs": [
      {
        "chapter": 1,
        "anchor": "瓦耳拉齐临死前的请求",
        "event_type": "resolution"
      }
    ],
    "rag_refs": [1]
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_012",
    "speaker": "char_wa_er_la_qi",
    "listener": "char_li_wen_xiu",
    "text": "阿秀，师父快死了，师父死了之后，就没人照顾你了。世界上的人都坏得很，大家只想害你，没人会真心的待你。你真心待人家好，也没有用的⋯⋯你一转头，人家就忘了你啦。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
